{"tid":1454731,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"【烏鴉外傳】《執行者》如何處決何妖？","createTime":"2019-08-12T08:13:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T15:48:26.000Z","uid":31827,"like":24,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"acb6804496650e603912a56591eb044f2a8fd670","tid":1454731,"uid":31827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:13:28.000Z","msg":"烏鴉習慣在黑房中工作，儘管他知道這樣對眼睛並不好。<br />\n<br />\n人們似乎錯了重點，因為政府想他們弄錯重點，所以他們的汪意力都放在popo上。當然popo是有罪的，但說到底他們不過是可憐的工具而已，要是沒有在上位者的默許，他們又哪來的勇氣？<br />\n<br />\n烏鴉不喜歡太快解決事情，他希望可以一步一步來，讓他能夠享受當中的樂趣。<br />\n<br />\n高官看著無奈的市民而高興；烏鴉看著無奈的高官而高興。<br />\n<br />\n這叫報應。<br />\n<br />\n想到這裡，烏鴉不禁又想笑。接下來要選擇的只有兩條路：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />折磨何妖<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一刀解決，眼不見為淨<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n－－－－－－<br />\n本故事純屬虛構"},{"pid":"474cac6ebfe24e9774b7f4b0dc06b0ab605b04ae","tid":1454731,"uid":137863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:14:26.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"1ceeeda3340618f1d177cddc8b80db5ca07b8006","tid":1454731,"uid":31827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:14:31.000Z","msg":"真係故事黎：<br />\nPOST1:<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/670661/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/670661/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"2d0abb7d0f9551e6bfcbdcd321683a0834cc3658","tid":1454731,"uid":29880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:14:44.000Z","msg":"以牙還牙,用返藤條鐵通"},{"pid":"0ed8d8b7eec45246b4037ccdd6e93b730698de92","tid":1454731,"uid":31827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:22:01.000Z","msg":"作者功績之一<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><em><span style=\"color: red;\">官黑勾結</span></em></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0yUUXWO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0yUUXWO.png&h=5fe8e826&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https: